name: Whistle! Dai 37-kai Tokyo-to Chuugakkou Sougou Taiiku Soccer Taikai
name_original: Whistle! Dai 37-kai Tokyo-to Chuugakkou Sougou Taiiku Soccer Taikai
description:
Whistle! Dai 37-kai Tokyo-to Chuugakkou Sougou Taiiku Soccer Taikai is a sports-arcade game developed by INTENSE. It was originally released in 2003. It was published by Konami.
You can play Whistle! Dai 37-kai Tokyo-to Chuugakkou Sougou Taiiku Soccer Taikai on Game Boy Advance.
